Was a member of Millburn’s basketball team who won the Conference Championship in 2010-11… Was named All-County Honorable Mention and All-Conference second team as a freshman… Was selected to the All-Conference and All-County second teams in her sophomore year… Received All-County first team honors and was selected All-Group third team as a junior… Was named All-County first team and All-Conference second team in her senior season...
